reviewText: Such easy listening!  What a great performance and what great voices.  The blend is spine tingling!  I am close to having all of their CD's and DVD's.  Could listen and watch them all day!

Great harmony and strong spiritual messages in this early Booth Brothers video.  The bonus features are among the best with the extra songs being some of the best of their work.  Notably clear with Ronnie and Jim providing guitar accompaniment.  Touching moments of personal testimony.
